{"ID":"20260609130748-x7fx7x4","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609130748-x7fx7x4","title":"2022年浙江卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609130807-8mbfe88","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130807-8mbfe88","updated":"20260609130808"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【甲】"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"翻开《精神的力量——航天精神引领中华民族探索浩瀚宇宙》一书，中国航天事业的历程一一展现，字里行间全是澎湃的热情，全是珍贵的回忆。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中国航天人自力更生、艰苦奋斗，航天事业从无到有、从小到大，迅速发展壮大。【乙】"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"我永远忘不了，从天上传来的“东方红”乐曲是那么悠扬、那样动听！"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"改革开放以来，党中央和全国人民继续大力支持航天事业，中国航天人披荆斩棘、刻苦攻关，航天事业穿云裂石，突飞猛进地实现飞跃，大踏步赶上时代。首次载人航天飞行，神舟五号载人飞船成功升空并安全返回，获得圆满成功；神舟七号载人飞船实施宇航员空间出舱活动。这一切无不给我们带来激动和幸福！进入新时代，航天梦引领中国航天人奋力奔跑、勇敢逐梦，让航天事业奔向强国目标，自立自强地谱写着新的辉煌篇章。【丙】"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"北斗泽沐八方，嫦娥飞天揽月，天问造访火星，天和筑梦天河……这些好消息一则接着一则地传来，很不容易，真是令人万般欣慰！"}]},{"ID":"20260609130812-t669wur","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609130812-t669wur","updated":"20260609130832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609130832-z9m9yth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130832-z9m9yth","updated":"20260609130832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．文段中的加点词语，运用不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609130832-0one1ab","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130832-0one1ab","updated":"20260609130832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．自力更生                    B．穿云裂石                    C．无不                              D．谱写"}]},{"ID":"20260609130832-4o1133a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130832-4o1133a","updated":"20260609130832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．文段中画线的甲、乙、丙句，标点有误的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609130832-g7as7j3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130832-g7as7j3","updated":"20260609130832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．甲                                                  B．乙                                                 C．丙"}]},{"ID":"20260609130748-nvsd9co","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609130748-nvsd9co","updated":"20260609130838"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609130748-bm3stke","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130748-bm3stke","updated":"20260609130838"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．B    3．B"}]},{"ID":"20260609130748-a3azi9c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609130748-a3azi9c","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-kudgq3g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-kudgq3g","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2．本题考查学生正确使用词语（包括成语）的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-ml0axdx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-ml0axdx","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“自力更生”，不依赖外力，靠自己的力量把事情办起来。形容中国航天人，使用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-2rgyukj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-2rgyukj","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“穿云裂石”，穿入云霄，震裂石头，形容声音高亢嘹亮。文中用来修饰“航天事业”，使用对象错误。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-iao0pb5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-iao0pb5","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“无不”，没有不，全是。文中是说航天事业所取得的一切成就都给人们带来了激动和幸福，使用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-ph67ynf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-ph67ynf","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.“谱写”，创作歌曲或为歌词配曲。也比喻用行动表现极其动人的英雄事迹(多和“凯歌”“诗篇”“篇章”一类词连用)。使用正确。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-w6g64mc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-w6g64mc","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-6ett068","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-6ett068","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3．本题考查学生正确使用标点的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-vyj6oy5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-vyj6oy5","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.乐曲名应使用书名号，所以“东方红”应为《东方红》。"}]},{"ID":"20260609130849-h9behff","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609130849-h9behff","updated":"20260609130849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]}]}